our membership.

334
00:15:27,570 --> 00:15:29,500
Now, on to the next.

335
00:15:29,500 --> 00:15:31,820
Gentleman number 9, Kawajiri-san.

336
00:15:31,820 --> 00:15:33,120
Yes.

337
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:37,050
Lady number 8, Nonomura-san.

338
00:15:37,050 --> 00:15:38,860
Oh... yes.

339
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:42,260
Congratulations.

340
00:15:42,260 --> 00:15:44,290
