347
00:16:00,470 --> 00:16:03,210
First, lady number 1.

348
00:16:03,210 --> 00:16:04,810
Kuramochi-san.

349
00:16:05,250 --> 00:16:06,110
Yes.

350
00:16:06,110 --> 00:16:08,310
Gentleman number 10.

351
00:16:08,310 --> 00:16:10,410
Hakamada-san.

352
00:16:10,940 --> 00:16:12,650
Congratulations!

353
00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:18,630
Isn't that nice?

354
00:16:16,530 --> 00:16:19,930
Sensei, too? But why?

355
00:16:20,530 --> 00:16:23,290
Hakamada-san. How do you feel?

356
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:27,410
I want our relationship to be warm,

357
00:16:27,410 --> 00:16:29,920
