358
00:16:32,470 --> 00:16:34,570
What an annoying analogy.

359
00:16:36,700 --> 00:16:39,110
Don't get carried away
because you got paired.

360
00:16:39,110 --> 00:16:41,500
This is just an investigation.

361
00:16:41,500 --> 00:16:43,050
Of course, I am aware of that.

362
00:16:43,050 --> 00:16:46,410
Kurumi-san, you're the one getting
carried away. You're seriously upset.

363
00:16:46,410 --> 00:16:48,300
I'm not upset at all.

364
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:51,900
Were you satisfied with the
marriage interview party?

365
00:16:51,900 --> 00:16:52,990
Ozaki-san.

366
00:16:53,810 --> 00:16:57,010
Are you trying to infiltrate us?

367
00:16:57,010 --> 00:16:59,030
I can't say I approve.

368
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:01,910
I will pretend this never happened,

369
00:17:01,910 --> 00:17:03,810
as long as you never do this again.

370
00:17:03,810 --> 00:17:06,500
You're making a nuisance
of yourselves to our members.

371
00:17:07,620 --> 00:17:09,350
I understand.

372
00:17:09,350 --> 00:17:10,710
I apologize.

373
