Hakamada
Law Office

374
00:17:23,520 --> 00:17:24,710
How did it go?

375
00:17:24,710 --> 00:17:25,720
Did you get paired?

376
00:17:25,720 --> 00:17:27,600
Well...

377
00:17:27,600 --> 00:17:29,920
That's not important.

378
00:17:29,920 --> 00:17:33,730
Sensei, don't get carried away
because you got paired up, too.

379
00:17:33,730 --> 00:17:35,400
I'm not getting carried away.

380
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:37,570
Sensei was paired?

381
00:17:37,570 --> 00:17:38,850
That's too weird.

382
00:17:38,850 --> 00:17:44,620
