384
00:17:47,040 --> 00:17:50,580
They're definitely suspicious, though.

385
00:17:50,580 --> 00:17:51,870
Indeed.

386
00:17:51,870 --> 00:17:54,330
They are on the lookout for us,

387
00:17:54,330 --> 00:17:57,030
so there's a high probability
they've got something to hide.

388
00:17:57,030 --> 00:17:59,590
That's where my investigation comes in.

389
00:18:00,600 --> 00:18:02,420
This case pertains to my client.

390
00:18:02,420 --> 00:18:05,060
Please follow my instructions.

391
00:18:08,390 --> 00:18:09,000
Oh.

392
00:18:09,820 --> 00:18:11,110
Who is it?

393
00:18:11,110 --> 00:18:13,410
The lady I was coupled with.

394
00:18:13,410 --> 00:18:16,280
You even exchanged phone numbers?

395
00:18:16,280 --> 00:18:17,570
Hello.

396
00:18:18,370 --> 00:18:20,230
It was nice meeting you today.

397
00:18:21,220 --> 00:18:22,570
Tonight?

398
00:18:23,130 --> 00:18:24,370
No.

399
00:18:24,370 --> 00:18:25,960
I'm not busy.

400
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:28,750
They're going on a date
right off the bat.

401
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:31,040
You see? He got carried away.

402
00:18:35,140 --> 00:18:36,160
Ah.

403
00:18:36,160 --> 00:18:39,420
Well, Kanae-san.

404
00:18:39,420 --> 00:18:41,050
Could that be your partner?

405
00:18:41,050 --> 00:18:42,480
Oh, yes.

406
00:18:42,480 --> 00:18:47,580
But, I'm going to properly explain
my situation, and turn him down.

407
00:18:49,480 --> 00:18:50,980
Wait a second!

408
00:18:50,980 --> 00:18:51,940
What?

409
00:18:51,940 --> 00:18:54,010
Your partner...

410
00:18:54,010 --> 00:18:56,480
Didn't he say he was
a long-time member?

411
00:19:00,360 --> 00:19:03,930
I was only participating in the
speed-dating party for research.

412
00:19:03,930 --> 00:19:05,840
I'm very sorry.

413
00:19:05,840 --> 00:19:07,690
I see.

414
00:19:08,350 --> 00:19:11,100
But you are single,
aren't you, Kanae-san?

415
00:19:11,100 --> 00:19:12,840
Well, yes...

416
00:19:12,840 --> 00:19:15,030
Even if it was just research,

417
00:19:15,030 --> 00:19:17,640
we've still managed
to meet each other.

418
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:21,760
Please date me,
with an eye toward marriage!

419
00:19:21,760 --> 00:19:23,040
I'm sorry.

420
00:19:23,040 --> 00:19:25,200
I don't care if you've got one strike.

421
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:26,870
I will embrace your past,
and love you and the whole package—

422
00:19:26,870 --> 00:19:28,020
I'm sorry.

423
00:19:28,820 --> 00:19:30,510
Please give up on her.

424
00:19:30,510 --> 00:19:31,510
Huh?

425
00:19:31,510 --> 00:19:35,960
I'm here today because I want you
to tell me about Get-Marriage.

426
00:19:35,960 --> 00:19:37,510
What do you want to know?

427
00:19:37,510 --> 00:19:40,870
Have you ever been
dissatisfied by them?

428
00:19:41,740 --> 00:19:44,090
They're very considerate.

429
00:19:44,090 --> 00:19:47,330
I'm registered with other
matchmaking establishments,

430
00:19:47,330 --> 00:19:50,330
but in comparison to the others,
they're warm and accommodating.

431
00:19:50,330 --> 00:19:52,880
Have you ever suspected
they might have planted fakes?

432
00:19:52,880 --> 00:19:54,530
I don't believe there's
anything like that.

433
00:19:54,530 --> 00:19:58,170
I've always gotten legitimate
responses from matches.

434
00:19:58,590 --> 00:20:01,310
Oh, but come to think of it,

435
00:20:01,310 --> 00:20:04,050
there was this one time
I got turned down.

436
00:20:04,050 --> 00:20:05,040
By whom?

437
00:20:06,580 --> 00:20:08,810
She's the chief editor
of a gourmet magazine.

438
00:20:08,810 --> 00:20:10,550
This was Yukawa Natsuko-san?

439
00:20:10,550 --> 00:20:12,550
That might've been her name—

440
00:20:12,550 --> 00:20:15,940
And who was the assistant at that time?

441
00:20:15,940 --> 00:20:18,150
His name was Tachibana-san.

442
00:20:37,540 --> 00:20:39,240
Hakamada Law Office

443
00:20:37,540 --> 00:20:39,240
You were being followed?

444
00:20:39,240 --> 00:20:41,450
Did you get a look at him?

445
00:20:42,130 --> 00:20:44,770
I could only see his back,

446
00:20:44,770 --> 00:20:46,880
so I can't be sure who he was...

447
00:20:48,570 --> 00:20:52,030
But I think that it was
Tachibana-san of Get-Marriage.

448
00:20:52,030 --> 00:20:53,640
Tachibana-san?

449
00:20:53,640 --> 00:20:57,070
Actually, this isn't the first
time something like this happened.

450
00:20:57,070 --> 00:20:58,470
Can you explain?

451
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:01,920
I've been followed several
times before, on my way home.

452
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:07,350
There was a man asking
about me at a local bar I frequent.

453
00:21:07,350 --> 00:21:10,430
You think Tachibana-san
has been doing these things?

454
00:21:11,270 --> 00:21:13,030
It's very possible.

455
00:21:13,840 --> 00:21:17,640
This was the first time I actually
saw him in person, though.

456
00:21:18,190 --> 00:21:20,480
I wonder what's they're scheming.

457
00:21:20,480 --> 00:21:22,520
We have testimony from a member

458
00:21:22,520 --> 00:21:27,290
that Tachibana-san has been obstructing
Natsuko-san from finding a partner.

459
00:21:27,290 --> 00:21:29,150
Tachibana-san...

460
00:21:32,150 --> 00:21:33,760
Excuse me for a moment.

461
00:21:36,630 --> 00:21:37,950
Hello.

462
00:21:37,950 --> 00:21:40,240
I enjoyed the visit.

463
00:21:40,240 --> 00:21:43,200
That must be his partner.

464
00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:45,730
He's totally immersed
in "get married" mode.

465
00:21:45,730 --> 00:21:48,650
Ah, that's it! Tachibana
has been following

466
00:21:48,650 --> 00:21:51,210
